[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "空灵，寂静，针落可闻。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "少女将身体蜷缩在精致考究的椅子里，用双手抱住双膝，直直地盯着地面。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在一束顶光的直射下，她抬起头，看向了与自己隔桌相对的一团黑影。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "然后，开始了梦呓一般的讲述。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_01",
        "zh_CN": "一年前……对，差不多就是一年前。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_02",
        "zh_CN": "我记得那是个阴天，没太阳，雾蒙蒙的。你裹得像个粽子，他……他也没好到哪儿去，缩在那个已经摔变形了的逃生舱里，还呆头呆脑的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_03",
        "zh_CN": "你知道吗，虽然在很多事情上我都一直输你一头，啊……当然了，后来人多起来了，在有些事情上也不只输给你一个。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_04",
        "zh_CN": "但有一件事我却对自己很有信心，一直有，而且一直能赢。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_05",
        "zh_CN": "衣品。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_06",
        "zh_CN": "……也不知道是不是因为这个世界实在太寡淡了，还是我自己本来就太渴望光鲜，喜欢一直把自己打扮得……闪耀一点？夺目一点？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_07",
        "zh_CN": "用从头到脚的每一个细节，去撑起一个骄傲的模样来……好像这样就能让自己打起精神来，去对抗所有的一切。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_08",
        "zh_CN": "狮子……他们是这样形容我的，对吧？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_09",
        "zh_CN": "哼，莫名其妙地就有了这么一个外号，但我只见过电子影像投射出来的，真正的狮子摸起来是什么手感，到现在我都不清楚。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_10",
        "zh_CN": "你知道吗，他曾经答应我，说早晚要找一头真的狮子来让我动手摸一摸。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_11",
        "zh_CN": "说什么……只要见过了，我就会知道自己在他人眼里到底是个什么样子。还说那样就能让我更坚定自己的本心本性，从小女孩儿变成……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_12",
        "zh_CN": "真是胡说八道……本小姐怎么可能会在乎别人的眼光！更何况，我难道还需要从一个已经灭绝了的动物身上学到点什么吗……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_13",
        "zh_CN": "骗子，笨蛋，满嘴跑火车……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_14",
        "zh_CN": "一开始还很木讷，老实，碰上那些喜欢欺负他的王八蛋，就只会温吞犹豫，摆出一副任人宰割的模样，也不知道是在顾虑什么。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_15",
        "zh_CN": "害得我整天担心他，变着花样儿哄着他……明明照单全收就好了，偏偏却还要退缩，若即若离的……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_16",
        "zh_CN": "真是一想起来就让本小姐火大！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_17",
        "zh_CN": "后来可倒好，相处的日子久了，本性暴露了，原来从始至终他什么都清楚明白！该对人下手的时候一点都不含糊。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_18",
        "zh_CN": "好勇斗狠，睚眦必报，一个大男人每天藏着一万个心眼儿……活的又累又拧巴。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_19",
        "zh_CN": "实在看不下去了想替他出头，他倒好，宁可自己再多受些委屈，也要先跑过来拦住我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_20",
        "zh_CN": "冠冕堂皇地说着什么家人，保护，遮风挡雨的肉麻腔调……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_21",
        "zh_CN": "见不得光的事情他自己来，轮到鲜花和掌声的时候就把我们推到前面去了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_22",
        "zh_CN": "名声，尊严，荣誉……本小姐是喜欢这些东西，但他怎么就不明白跟那些无谓的褒赞比起来，我更想要的是他……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_23",
        "zh_CN": "为知己者死，为悦己者容。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_24",
        "zh_CN": "海姆达尔的黄金狮子，以这种新的立场和身份活着之后，本小姐的确……再也没有输给过任何人！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_25",
        "zh_CN": "但这种胜利到了最近却建立在由他自己冲在前面，代替我去跟越来越歹毒危险的敌人作战的前提下……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_26",
        "zh_CN": "直到今天。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_27",
        "zh_CN": "喂，好歹说句话吧，星期三？别让我一个人在这里念叨好不好？我……我还不想被人当成是人老珠黄，喜欢碎碎念的……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl002b_01",
        "zh_CN": "你想让我说什么。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "藏于阴影中的她倏然间开口，冰冷的语调里满是不容置喙的威仪。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_28",
        "zh_CN": "我们刚刚……失去分析员了，是吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl002b_02",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_29",
        "zh_CN": "你，我，我们两个，刚刚眼睁睁地看着那个女人把分析员给——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl002b_03",
        "zh_CN": "对，没错。罗赞·赫瓦雷纳在我们面前，把分析员从这座浮空城上给扔下去了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_30",
        "zh_CN": "为什么会发生这种事？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl002b_04",
        "zh_CN": "你说呢？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_31",
        "zh_CN": "是因为我不够强，动作不够快，没来得及在那座酒店里就把分析员给救出来吗……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl002b_05",
        "zh_CN": "对。你慢了，你没能阻止罗赞带走他。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_32",
        "zh_CN": "也因为我没有力量……像你现在所拥有的那种力量，所以刚刚才没办法突破到敌人面前，把他抢回来？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl002b_06",
        "zh_CN": "嗯。你被那些杂碎绊住脚步了，脱了节。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_33",
        "zh_CN": "我……输了？我真的输了……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl002b_07",
        "zh_CN": "输了。在最重要的事情上输了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_34",
        "zh_CN": "……！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "少女不明白，眼前的人怎么可以用这样云淡风轻的姿态说出这些真相……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "明明自己只是坐在这里，就能真切地感受到对方身上那莫大的愤怒和痛苦。明明对方此时应该远比自己还要更伤心欲绝，更疯魔痴狂才对……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_35",
        "zh_CN": "你现在到底是里芙，还是……奥丁？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl002b_08",
        "zh_CN": "你呢？说出这些话，你是芬妮·戈尔登吗。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "像是陡然间把一块软木塞楔进了自己的喉咙里……她被对方这一句话问得哑口无言。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl002b_09",
        "zh_CN": "你知道我现在在想什么吗。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl002b_10",
        "zh_CN": "我在想这是哪儿？什么地方？我们两个到底为什么会出现在这里，又在等待着什么。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_36",
        "zh_CN": "这重要吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl002b_11",
        "zh_CN": "重要。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_37",
        "zh_CN": "很重要？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl002b_12",
        "zh_CN": "很重要。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 58,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl002b_13",
        "zh_CN": "因为只有弄清楚了才能知道之前发生的那一切，你正害怕着的那一切……到底是不是真的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 59,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl008b_38",
        "zh_CN": "我不明白。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 60,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc9st2_girl002b_14",
        "zh_CN": "我也不明白。所以得让明白的家伙滚出来，自己亲口解释给我们听。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 61,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "怒目圆睁，长身而立，她从包裹着自己的那团阴影中现身，用雷光将眼前原本黑暗迷蒙的空间瞬息照亮。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 62,
        "Flag": "",
